OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on plans to
OL,7,Frestructure Torbay Council's
OL,8,Fchildren's services
OL,10,FTorbay Council is planning a major
OL,11,Fshake-up of its children's services
OL,12,Fdepartment, with some jobs at risk, in
OL,13,Fan effort to save #3 million per year
OL,14,Fand fit in with new Government
OL,15,Fguidelines.
OL,17,FITV West Country understands the
OL,18,Fchanges could mean possible
OL,19,Fredundancies, which could affect
OL,20,Fsocial workers and managers who
OL,21,Foversee SEND care plans.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,FThe council has been accused of making
OL,7,Fdecisions 'behind closed doors', and
OL,8,Fparents are worried about how this
OL,9,Fwill impact on children who need help.
OL,11,FStefanie Curran, whose two sons have
OL,12,Fbeen diagnosed with autism, said: "My
OL,13,Fchildren are very bright, they're very
OL,14,Fcapable. They just need a little bit
OL,15,Fof extra support. But to get that is
OL,16,Fsuch a battle.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,F"It's very frustrating that their
OL,7,Feducation is just wasting away,
OL,8,Fopportunities are being made so hard
OL,9,Ffor them when they have a legal right
OL,10,Fto an education."
OL,12,FTorbay Council's children's services
OL,13,Fdepartment is under an Ofsted
OL,14,F'improvement notice', and staff are
OL,15,Funderstood to be under 'intense
OL,16,Fpressure' to perform better.
OL,18,F"It's the delays," Stefanie said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,F"You ask for something, and it takes
OL,7,Fweeks to get a response. Then you
OL,8,Freply, and it's weeks again.
OL,10,F"I feel it's very deliberate. I think
OL,11,Fthey're aware that every day they
OL,12,Fdon't reply is a day saved on
OL,13,Feducation, they're not having to spend
OL,14,Fon it. Every day for us is a day
OL,15,Fmissed."
OL,17,FThe council has told staff it needs to
OL,18,Fsave #3 million a year from children's
OL,19,Fservices, and is planning a major
OL,20,Frestructure of the department to fit
OL,21,Fin with national government guidance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,FInternal documents seen by ITV West
OL,7,FCountry suggest this could involve
OL,8,Fmerging teams, possible redundancies,
OL,9,Fdeleting vacant posts and changes to
OL,10,Fmanagement structures.
OL,12,FThe number of Independent Reviewing
OL,13,FOfficers - social workers who oversee
OL,14,Fcare plans for children - could be
OL,15,Fcut, and replaced by a centralised
OL,16,Fmulti-agency child protection team.
OL,18,FParents fear this could reduce
OL,19,Ffrontline capacity for families in
OL,20,Fneed, at a time when the council is
OL,21,Falready struggling to help everyone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,FStefanie added: "To me, it feels like
OL,7,Fchange for change's sake. There's a
OL,8,Flot of shifting around of jobs.
OL,9,FThey've got to make these huge savings.
OL,11,F"I just don't see how it's going to
OL,12,Fmake any real difference, because
OL,13,Fultimately they're keeping the people
OL,14,Fthe same.
OL,16,F"If you have a very toxic culture, and
OL,17,Fa culture of people who aren't working
OL,18,Fefficiently, what's really going to
OL,19,Fchange other than the job title?"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,FTorbay's Liberal Democrat MP, Steve
OL,7,FDarling, has accused the council of a
OL,8,Flack of transparency.
OL,10,F"I'm really worried about this," Mr
OL,11,FDarling said.
OL,13,F"Children deserve better in Torbay.
OL,14,FThis is all happening behind closed
OL,15,Fdoors, without scrutiny, without
OL,16,Fpeople like myself and fellow Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrat councillors being able to
OL,18,Fhold them to account.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,F"So we are making serious enquiries
OL,7,Fbecause we are really worried about
OL,8,Fwhat is going on behind closed doors."
OL,10,FA spokesman for Torbay Council told
OL,11,Fus: "In line with the Department for
OL,12,FEducation's 'Families First
OL,13,FPartnership' transformation
OL,14,Finitiative, we are currently
OL,15,Fconsulting with our staff on some
OL,16,Fproposed changes to our children's
OL,17,Fservices structure. The consultation
OL,18,Fis at a very early and sensitive stage
OL,19,Fso we are not in a position to comment
OL,20,Ffurther."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784272687
OL,3,CJobs at risk as council plans shake-up
OL,4,Cof children's services department
OL,6,FIf the changes go ahead, the new
OL,7,Fstructure is expected to be in place
OL,8,Fby the autumn.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
